      "content": "i know, i'm being careful but it just hurts so bad i can't even sit down. i checked online and some people say you can take more if it's for bad pain. like, if i took another 800mg of the ibu in a bit, would that be okay? it's just for tonight so i can get some sleep, it's not like i'm gonna do it every day.",
